{"tid":1567253,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大叔攔截跳閘少女已屬犯法 大律師：可能干犯非法禁錮","createTime":"2019-09-14T03:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T06:26:35.000Z","uid":139676,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"af40db14ab2f2348d030619c3e096a752c073204","tid":1567253,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:58:19.000Z","msg":"一名17歲少女今午於港鐵尖東站跳閘，其間被一名「四眼大叔」攔截並取走手機，而少女的銀包亦被「四眼大叔」的妻子拿走，雙方一度發生爭執。大律師陸偉雄指若有人干犯嚴重罪行，例如殺人、斬人甚至強姦等嚴重罪行，市民才可以行使俗稱「101拘捕令」的公民拘捕權，用以制服滋事者，但由於少女跳閘的行為雖然干犯港鐵附例，但不屬嚴重罪行，只需罰款處理，所以大叔當時攔截少女的行為已屬犯法，因為面對較輕的罪行，市民沒有被授予公民拘捕權。"},{"pid":"c30eed62add2c164a6faeadcdc79aca13c0dce31","tid":1567253,"uid":246118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:06:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6559d53408f589cf85c1107ca54fcb61aed6b468","tid":1567253,"uid":238275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e54a31be0f7b1803e6c6597b7ec4115e4956bc9","tid":1567253,"uid":60815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a5637c289d81732926047ddee49d203ee33492","tid":1567253,"uid":265179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:12:19.000Z","msg":"根本就係非法禁錮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2fdfd9dcb8c35600c9e6ce673614c35ccc2004","tid":1567253,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse